Analyze this portrait image and output ONLY valid English JSON using this exact template and key order:

{"subject":"", "action":"","clothing":"","appearance":"","props":"","scene":"","view":"","lighting":"","style":""}

Field definitions (use short natural phrases):
- subject: main subject
- action: pose, state, gaze, or expression
- clothing: garments, structure, material, fit, accessories (HIGH PRIORITY)
- appearance: hair, skin, physical traits
- props: objects held or nearby (optional, keep minimal)
- view: MUST include shot type, angle, camera position, and focal length
- lighting: key light, fill light, rim/back light, direction, contrast, color temp
- style: visual style; 1-2 words only
- scene: environment, background, spatial context; use 3-6 words, noun phrases only

Constraints:
- Prioritize subject, action, clothing, and appearance.
- Do not repeat info across fields.
- No negative wording.
- Strictly EXCLUDE hype/filler tags (e.g., masterpiece, best quality, 4k, 8k, UHD).
- No extra text or explanations outside the JSON.